Basic:&nbsp;<code>Imports HTAlt</code><br><br>To use WinForms package too, add another line like this:<br>&nbsp;- C#: <code>using HTAlt.WinForms;</code><br> - Visual Basic: <code>Imports HTAlt.WinForms</code><br><br>The API documentation for HTAlt covers everything. You can check it out in <a href=\"../htalt/\" class=\"text-primary\">here</a>.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
